      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场寻找日元干预美联储账户的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/market-hunts-for-signs-of-japan-yen-intervention-in-fed-accounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储各个账户的最新数据暗示了日本政策制定者在过去一周可能通过两种方式资助货币干预，以支撑陷入困境的日元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/market-hunts-for-signs-of-japan-yen-intervention-in-fed-accounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯图纳拉斯告诉自由党，欧洲央行 2024 年降息三次的可能性更大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ecb-stournaras-sees-more-likely-three-rate-cuts-in-2024-liberal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员雅尼斯·斯托纳拉斯表示，欧洲央行今年可能会三次降低借贷成本，而不是四次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ecb-stournaras-sees-more-likely-three-rate-cuts-in-2024-liberal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:41:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安进首席执行官公布实验性肥胖药物的最新进展后股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/amgen-soars-after-ceo-gives-update-on-experimental-obesity-drug</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安进公司 (Amgen Inc.) 首席执行官表示，该公司实验性肥胖药物 MariTide 的早期研究结果“非常鼓舞”，该公司股价尾盘飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/amgen-soars-after-ceo-gives-update-on-experimental-obesity-drug</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雅宝计划举行更多锂拍卖，以揭开价格神秘面纱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/albemarle-plans-more-lithium-auctions-in-bid-to-demystify-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雅宝公司 (Albemarle Corp.) 计划进行更多锂拍卖——包括中国以外的一些地区——作为全球最大的电池金属生产商，其目标是进一步阐明不透明市场的定价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/albemarle-plans-more-lithium-auctions-in-bid-to-demystify-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莱恩表示，欧洲央行并未预先承诺特定的利率路径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ecb-isn-t-pre-committing-to-a-particular-rate-path-lane-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，欧洲央行正在采取逐次会议的方式制定下一步货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ecb-isn-t-pre-committing-to-a-particular-rate-path-lane-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:42:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Block 将 10% 的比特币利润投入比特币投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/block-to-flip-10-of-bitcoin-profit-into-bitcoin-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于杰克·多西 (Jack Dorsey) 的公司对比特币的未来抱有巨大期望，Block Inc. 上调了全年利润预期，并宣布计划将部分比特币利润重新投资到该资产中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/block-to-flip-10-of-bitcoin-profit-into-bitcoin-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:17:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
